data.description:
Welcome to 1829 S Cindy Ct, a hidden gem nestled in the idyllic cul-de-sac of Visalia's Southwest neighborhood. Boasting three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this residence spans approximately 1377 square feet and sits on an expansive 6481 square foot lot—a canvas awaiting your creative touch.

As you approach this charming abode, the quiet serenity of the cul-de-sac envelopes you, offering a sense of peaceful seclusion. The potential within this property is vast, making it an ideal investment opportunity for astute investors or a perfect canvas for a buyer with a vision for a personalized fixer-upper.

The generously sized lot not only provides ample space for gardening, outdoor entertainment, and play but also offers an opportunity for potential expansion and customization, ensuring this residence can grow with your aspirations.

Inside, a spacious floor plan invites you to reimagine the space and tailor it to your taste and lifestyle. The three bedrooms provide a versatile layout for families, professionals, or creative individuals seeking a comfortable living arrangement.

Whether you envision modern upgrades or retain the classic charm, this residence is a perfect platform to showcase your unique style and elevate it into a haven of your dreams. With thoughtful renovations, you can transform this house into a home that echoes your personality and preferences.

Located on the Southwest side of Visalia, convenience is at your fingertips with easy access to schools, shopping centers, dining, and recreational facilities. Embrace the opportunity to explore the vibrant community and create a lifestyle that suits you.

1829 S Cindy Ct represents more than just a house—it's a canvas awaiting your creative strokes, a place where dreams can be nurtured and aspirations realized. Don't miss the chance to make this residence your own and craft a story within its walls.

Contact us today to schedule a viewing and embark on the exciting journey.
